1023361,188,545,69,129,1,466,48,"‘‘ Kiṃ panettha yutticintāya, ācariyassa idha kamavacanicchā natthīti evametaṃ gahetabbaṃ– aññāsupi hi aṭṭhakathāsu ayameva anukkamo vutto, na ca tāsu‘ tena samayena verañjāyaṃ viharatī’ ti vinayapāḷipade hetuatthasseva sātisayaṃ adhippetabhāvadīpanatthaṃ vutto avisayattā, sikkhāpadāni paññāpayanto hetubhūtena, karaṇabhūtena ca samayena vihāsi, sikkhāpadapaññattihetuñca apekkhamāno hetubhūtena samayena vihāsīti evamettha yathālābhaṃ sambandhabhāvato evaṃ vutto’’ tipi vadanti. "
